snippet.title: Slayers X: Terminal Aftermath: Vengance of the Slayer: Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
click the WISH LIST button: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1931020/Slayers_X_Terminal_Aftermath_Vengance_of_the_Slayer/

sign up to take the SLAYERS PACT and PLAY EARLY: https://forms.gle/MrENE3k8JJ1b9amu6

Become ....AN X SLAYER: https://discord.com/invite/pQP8JvnSBj

So.... got what it takes to be a X Slayer?!?... 7 weapons, blood and gore, twisted music by Seepage & Psyko Syndikate, and maps where you can blow up everything. its awesome. started making it in 1998 in high school with my friend and now im 37, so i have life experience now.
